title: Everyone Hates Me Again - H3TV #25
description: Today we discuss one of mankind's greatest evolutionary questions...which big animals could you take in a fist fight? Lion? Bear? Eagle? The philosophical debates are endless. We also respond to the controversy surrounding Ethan's latest cancellation, & much much more. Jump on in yall
